OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FA host of people from Northern Ireland
OL,7,Fhave been recognised in the King's
OL,8,FBirthday Honours.
OL,10,FA wide range have been honoured for
OL,11,Fthe contribution they have made to
OL,12,Fsociety, from business and
OL,13,Fbroadcasting, to recovering the
OL,14,Fremains of the Disappeared, charity
OL,15,Fwork and agriculture.
OL,17,FAn MBE has been awarded to a "leading
OL,18,Fvoice" in research into ending
OL,19,Fviolence against women and girls.
OL,26,@yD@^OUzD@FO]
