OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FUlster University academic Dr Susan
OL,7,FLagdon was singled out for her
OL,8,F"exceptional contribution to advancing
OL,9,Funderstanding and prevention of gender-
OL,10,Fbased violence in Northern Ireland".
OL,12,FIt comes as statistics highlight the
OL,13,Fissue, with 31,558 domestic abuse
OL,14,Fincidents recorded by police in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland in the year to March
OL,16,F31 2026, an increase of 6.1% on the
OL,17,Fprevious year.
OL,19,FThe Dean of Enniskillen and the Co
OL,20,FFermanagh town's parish priest both
OL,21,Fhave been made OBEs.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
