OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FThe Very Rev Kenneth Hall and
OL,7,FMonsignor Peter O'Reilly, who lead
OL,8,Fchurches located opposite each other,
OL,9,Fmade a very public show of unity in
OL,10,F2012 when they jointly hosted Queen
OL,11,FElizabeth on a visit to the town.
OL,13,FThey said they are accepting in
OL,14,Frecognition of all those who over many
OL,15,Fyears through Northern Ireland's
OL,16,Fbattle with division, have chosen
OL,17,Ffriendship over suspicion, and hope
OL,18,Fover fear.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
