OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FUTV broadcaster Rose Neill said she is
OL,7,F"genuinely surprised and grateful" to
OL,8,Fbe been awarded an MBE.
OL,10,FShe said: "I feel privileged to
OL,11,Freceive this honour. I have learned so
OL,12,Fmuch from some wonderful colleagues in
OL,13,Ftelevision news over 49 years at both
OL,14,FUTV and BBC.
OL,16,F"I have also been inspired by lots of
OL,17,Fgenuine people in various charitable
OL,18,Forganisations over the years," she
OL,19,Fadded.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781608793
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,F"I love being part of such a helpful,
OL,7,Fprofessional, hard-working and happy
OL,8,Fteam at UTV. Collectively, they
OL,9,Fdeserve a great deal of credit
OL,10,Fthemselves.
OL,12,F"My sons, sister and my dear friends
OL,13,Fhave also supported me during my
OL,14,Fcareer."
OL,16,FBert Deane, an investigator with the
OL,17,FIndependent Commission for the
OL,18,FLocation of Victims' Remains (ICLVR)
OL,19,Fwhich works to find the remaining
OL,20,Fmembers of the Disappeared, has been
OL,21,Fmade an OBE.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781608793
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,F"It has been a huge privilege to have
OL,7,Fworked with the Independent Commission
OL,8,Ffor the Location of Victims' Remains
OL,9,Fand especially to get to know the
OL,10,Ffamilies of the Disappeared," he said.
OL,12,F"My heart goes out to those still
OL,13,Fwaiting to have their loved ones found
OL,14,Fand I know everyone in the ICLVR will
OL,15,Fdo all they can to help end their
OL,16,Fsuffering."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@]O]tD@AOUxD@KO]
