OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FA former head of the Ulster Farmers'
OL,7,FUnion (UFU) has said he is
OL,8,F"optimistic" about the future of the
OL,9,Findustry as he is recognised for
OL,10,Fservices to agriculture.
OL,12,FWesley Aston first joined the UFU in
OL,13,F1991 as a policy officer, becoming a
OL,14,Fpolicy director in 1995, also taking
OL,15,Fon the role of secretary to the dairy
OL,16,Fcommittee during the de-regulation of
OL,17,Fmilk marketing boards.
OL,19,FHe became chief executive in 2015, a
OL,20,Frole he held for more than a decade
OL,21,Fbefore standing down earlier this year.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
