OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FMr Aston said he is "surprised and
OL,7,Fdelighted" to be made an MBE.
OL,9,FFormer Crown Solicitor for Northern
OL,10,FIreland Jennifer Bell has been made a
OL,11,Fcompanion of the Order of the Bath for
OL,12,Fservices to the administration of
OL,13,Fjustice.
OL,15,FJoe O'Neill, chief executive of
OL,16,FBelfast Harbour, has been made a
OL,17,FCommander of the Order of the British
OL,18,FEmpire (CBE) for services to both
OL,19,Fbusiness and the community.
OL,26,@nD@UOUoD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
