OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FMr O'Neill said he was honoured to be
OL,7,Facknowledged.
OL,9,FHe said: "This is a moment of great
OL,10,Fpride, not only for myself, but for
OL,11,Fthe passionate and dedicated people
OL,12,Fwho are working hard to make Belfast
OL,13,FHarbour a success, ensuring that as a
OL,14,Fcity and region we can continue to
OL,15,Fthrive.
OL,26,@qD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
