OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1781608793
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,F"In addition, I would like to
OL,7,Frecognise those working in the third
OL,8,Fsector organisations I have been
OL,9,Finvolved with, particularly The Simon
OL,10,FCommunity, who have a significant
OL,11,Fimpact on those most in need in our
OL,12,Fcommunity."
OL,14,FBBC sports journalist and broadcaster
OL,15,FStephen Watson is also among those
OL,16,Fhonoured.
OL,18,FMr Watson described being told of his
OL,19,FMBE as a "bit of a shock".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@KO]{D@JOU{D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
