OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,FIt is recognition of decades of work
OL,7,Fin sports broadcasting, but also of
OL,8,Fhis support for transplant charities
OL,9,Fafter he spoke publicly about
OL,10,Freceiving a kidney transplant almost a
OL,11,Fdecade ago.
OL,13,F"Whilst it has come as a great
OL,14,Fsurprise to me, I am truly honoured
OL,15,Fand humbled to receive this MBE," Mr
OL,16,FWatson said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
