OL,3,CNorthern Ireland faces on King's
OL,4,CBirthday Honours list 2026
OL,6,F"I accept this honour with enormous
OL,7,Fgratitude and share it with my family,
OL,8,Fcolleagues, the charities I work
OL,9,Falongside, and the many people whose
OL,10,Fgenerosity and courage inspire me
OL,11,Fevery day."
